Comment: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:41.27,Opening Kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{Opening Start Frame}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:00.97,0:00:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you watch that show on TV yesterday?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.94,0:00:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What show?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.69,0:00:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one worth watching!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.26,0:00:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Reporter on the scene! Hamana Lake's \NGiant Eel — Hassie's Shocking Identity."
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.98,0:00:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I watched that too!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.53,0:00:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way it's real.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.17,0:00:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghosts are nothing but figments of our imagination. Right, Houtarou?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.78,0:00:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a boring guy. Isn't there a romantic in you?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.01,0:00:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Chii?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.07,0:00:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm curious as to whether or not it actually exists. The truth.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.13,0:00:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't care if they really exist, but I hope we see one today.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.95,0:00:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't that be fun?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.92,0:00:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghosts are nothing but figments of our imagination.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.18,0:00:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what I expected to hear from you.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.77,0:02:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Kamiyama High's Classic Literature Club has four members in total.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.79,0:02:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we all riding in a transit bus, you ask?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.77,0:02:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is obviously our destination.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.22,0:02:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our final stop is Zaizen Village.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.89,0:02:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's well known for hiking and hot springs.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.77,0:02:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're coming for the hot springs and not for hiking.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.69,0:02:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be doing anything during my \Nsummer break if I was living by my motto, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.69,0:02:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much for solving the mystery of my uncle!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.61,0:02:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we all visit a hot spring?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.37,0:02:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to a hot spring!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.25,0:02:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O—Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.19,0:02:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shuttle bus should be here to pick us up soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.85,0:02:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice view!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.48,0:02:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki, are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.66,0:02:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm car sick.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.86,0:02:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Houtarou.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.34,0:02:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our ride was only an hour and a half long.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.15,0:03:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so pathetic.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.24,0:03:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you were able to find us a place, Mayaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.02,0:03:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My relative who runs an inn is letting us stay for free. They're renovating right now and have spare rooms.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.18,0:03:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here, Oreki.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.30,0:03:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! We're finally here!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.76,0:03:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, or we'll leave you behind.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.76,0:03:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we come! Our inn!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.26,0:03:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Blue Mountain Resort!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.27,0:03:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the big sister, Zenna Rie,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.53,0:03:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she's the little sister, Zenna Kayo.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.23,0:03:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.31,0:03:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in sixth and fourth grade. You've grown agai—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.19,0:03:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your rooms are at the end of the second floor!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.57,0:03:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Check this out, Houtarou!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.66,0:03:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This room's got a pretty nice view, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.76,0:03:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess an occasional trip isn't all that bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.51,0:03:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've preferred to come here alone though.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.23,0:04:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, going a a trip by yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.48,0:04:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be joking!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.19,0:04:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just remember that we're here because of \NChitanda's planning and Mayaka's connections. {Magitek: I left this line a little ambiguous because the original sounded strange. Original line was: Don't forget, we're here because Chitanda planned it and Mayaka used her connections."}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.69,0:04:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for dinner.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.87,0:04:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come eat!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.27,0:04:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear that?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.75,0:04:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.57,0:04:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheese?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.98,0:04:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be stew? Gratin? Fondue?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chilled shabu-shabu?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.94,0:04:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready? Let's eat!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.71,0:04:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have dessert too.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.86,0:04:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheesecake?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.82,0:04:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.92,0:04:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I smelled it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.30,0:04:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.77,0:04:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.75,0:04:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's exactly like Maya said!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.25,0:04:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you tell them, Ibara?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.84,0:04:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's light some fireworks tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.86,0:04:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.58,0:04:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? My dad bought some yesterda—
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.14,0:04:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.67,0:04:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Sis.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.93,0:04:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.36,0:04:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.64,0:04:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you didn't burn yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.65,0:05:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.28,0:05:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, be careful!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.61,0:05:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so full.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.03,0:05:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi already went for a dip?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.38,0:05:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're at a hot spring resort, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.76,0:05:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Oreki?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.55,0:05:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same place as you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Ibara?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.24,0:05:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's occupied with the kids.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.51,0:05:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the sudden question, but what's your sister like?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.97,0:05:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that really is sudden.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.05,0:05:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're an only child, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.62,0:05:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.86,0:05:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's strange and incredible in many ways.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.90,0:05:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{doumo}I couldn't ever beat her in anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.99,0:05:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.62,0:05:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I ever wanted to.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.32,0:06:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you ask about my sister anyway?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.27,0:06:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it because you saw the Zenna Sisters?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.15,0:06:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I've always wished for siblings.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.78,0:06:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A big sister or a little brother.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.31,0:06:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's wonderful to always have someone close to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.39,0:06:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.49,0:06:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the princess is a bit too naive.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.74,0:06:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's living in a fantasy world.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.53,0:06:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In reality, siblings aren't wonderful at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.45,0:06:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mixed bathing here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.99,0:06:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi's here?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.67,0:06:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Dad and Grandpa!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.83,0:06:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.35,0:06:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! This place is bigger than I thought!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.94,0:07:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Houtarou.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.45,0:07:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally here.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.65,0:07:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The water here is really nice!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.95,0:07:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really improves your blood circulation!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.50,0:07:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be dangerous if the {\i1}water{\i0}  mixed with my blood!{he thinks water mixing with the blood instead of temperature improving circulation??}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.14,0:07:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.83,0:07:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to see you're relaxing though.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.51,0:07:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Chitanda?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.08,0:08:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki? What happened?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.34,0:08:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.51,0:08:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heat got to him.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.52,0:08:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.33,0:08:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just pathetic.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.63,0:08:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was there for twice as long as he was, but he passed out when I glanced over.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.74,0:08:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y—You're just so...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.76,0:08:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.51,0:08:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.30,0:08:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're destined to miss fun events.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.77,0:08:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.47,0:08:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Car sickness may have played a part in it too.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.63,0:08:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sick.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.96,0:08:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Chitanda?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.19,0:09:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.53,0:09:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.60,0:09:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still feverish.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.60,0:09:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I get you a cold towel?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.27,0:09:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I don't need it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.98,0:09:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.21,0:09:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for ruining our trip.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.07,0:09:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't ruining it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.68,0:09:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to share ghost stories.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.91,0:09:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come over if you start feeling better.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.88,0:09:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care then.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.98,0:09:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.73,0:09:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even 8 PM yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.25,0:09:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drumbeats?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.03,0:09:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We actually didn't need an annex.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other room's window is open too?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.79,0:09:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a secret.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A secret?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.45,0:10:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A creepy guest came to stay here a few years ago,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.66,0:10:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he stayed in room seven of the main building.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.94,0:10:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't want food or anyone to change his bed sheets.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.02,0:10:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't want anyone to come inside.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.83,0:10:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it ended up working out. He had already paid for his room and it was a busy season.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.00,0:10:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there was a horrible scream that night.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.89,0:10:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A scream?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.87,0:10:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone saw the shadow of a \Nswinging corpse dangling by the neck!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.06,0:10:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guest escaped to our resort after embezzling money from his company!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.52,0:10:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.42,0:10:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.68,0:10:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then, the guests who stayed in room seven
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.69,0:10:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,claimed there was something in the room, and they still see shadows at night!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.14,0:10:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then there's the ninth guest.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.65,0:10:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.88,0:10:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.33,0:10:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He died from a sudden illness!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.75,0:10:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was waiting for!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.90,0:10:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.47,0:11:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandma had the room exorcised and built the annex
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.46,0:11:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that rumors wouldn't spread.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.43,0:11:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's room seven?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.26,0:11:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that room directly across from our window.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.60,0:11:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We live on the first floor, and try to avoid the second floor.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.72,0:11:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.73,0:11:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our secret, okay? Promise?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.45,0:11:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so clichéd.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.69,0:11:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.98,0:11:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's morning already.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.75,0:12:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.99,0:12:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the others?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.53,0:12:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.33,0:12:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.26,0:12:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night I woke up to a warm breeze.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.19,0:12:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to turn in my sleep. That's when I saw the shadow of a hanging man.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.04,0:12:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was swaying and had a hazy glow!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.60,0:12:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not every day that you see Ibara so frightened.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.29,0:12:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish Satoshi was here to see this.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.45,0:12:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.60,0:12:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was the bath?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.33,0:12:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was great!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.09,0:12:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you liked it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.95,0:12:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The futon was soft too, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.48,0:12:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I slept really well!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.98,0:12:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see one for Kayo.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.74,0:12:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew those sort of stories scared you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.78,0:12:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not afraid of ghosts!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.61,0:12:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what I saw was just too creepy!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.33,0:12:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really see it?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.33,0:12:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did. I'm certain of it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.88,0:13:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you tell them? Dad said not to tell anyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.71,0:13:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Who cares? It's Maya!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.37,0:13:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.65,0:13:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what do you think of Maya's story?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.98,0:13:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hanging shadow?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.74,0:13:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, clichéd stories like that are passed down because people love them.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.00,0:13:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So do you think what Mayaka said was the truth?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.66,0:13:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.89,0:13:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I mistaken as well?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.03,0:13:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.96,0:13:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also saw that hanging shadow.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.87,0:13:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayaka woke up, and that woke me up too.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.32,0:13:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I saw it in the darkness.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.57,0:13:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.30,0:13:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I might have imagined it, but Mayaka saw the same thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.31,0:13:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have mistaken it for something else.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.68,0:13:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said yesterday, ghosts are nothing but...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.52,0:13:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...figments of our imagination?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.15,0:14:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's true, what was it that we saw?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.76,0:14:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.24,0:14:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you tell us what we mistook it for?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.99,0:14:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.06,0:14:11.33,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find out,  Oreki!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.33,0:14:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm curious!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.12,0:14:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Chii!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.58,0:14:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised to help out with their summer homework.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.50,0:14:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to us.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.10,0:14:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll definitely discover the truth.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.62,0:14:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Oreki?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.67,0:14:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, "always rush through the things that you have to do".
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.01,0:14:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you saw this shadow directly across from your room?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.27,0:14:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I did.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.99,0:14:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How big was the apparition?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.88,0:14:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was about the size of a normal person.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.69,0:14:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shape?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.79,0:14:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't clearly remember it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.57,0:14:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the color?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.29,0:14:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. I only saw its shadow.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.29,0:14:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.45,0:14:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were looking against the light, so you only saw someone's shadow, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.24,0:14:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.74,0:14:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Against the light.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.08,0:14:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The main source of light at night has to be the moon.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.33,0:14:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so too.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.15,0:15:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon was pretty bright last night.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.15,0:15:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it...?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.96,0:15:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chitanda, how long after the ghost stories did you go to sleep?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.22,0:15:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was 10 PM.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.72,0:15:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the shutters at the time?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.99,0:15:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe they were closed.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.17,0:15:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow couldn't have appeared if the shutters were closed.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.67,0:15:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's troubling.{consistency with "Would it be troubling if we can't go into Room 7?" later}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.21,0:15:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to take a look at room seven in the main building.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.06,0:15:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great! Mysteries!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.48,0:15:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we had this trip!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.57,0:15:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.27,0:15:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.91,0:15:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.65,0:15:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you handle this? I'm bad with kids.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.52,0:15:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.41,0:15:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo! Can I talk to you for a minute?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.18,0:15:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to the main building.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.75,0:15:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The main building? Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.70,0:15:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're investigating the hanging shadow.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.96,0:15:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we see room seven?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.38,0:15:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.40,0:15:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go in there right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.52,0:16:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister will get mad.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.22,0:16:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then just tell me one thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.18,0:16:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it still a guest room now?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.48,0:16:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.51,0:16:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the baths and the cafeteria in the main building are used by guests.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.45,0:16:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a vacant room, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.37,0:16:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As of right now, the second floor is used for storage.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.33,0:16:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.97,0:16:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks. You have been very helpfu—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.83,0:16:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She hates me.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.89,0:16:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. I'm sure she's just scared by tall guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.14,0:16:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be a problem if we can't go into room seven?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.59,0:16:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more troublesome than problematic.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.82,0:16:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we can't see where it actually happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.14,0:16:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I remember these!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.27,0:16:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning stretches...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.36,0:16:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to do these up until two years ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.50,0:16:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until she was in eighth grade?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.43,0:16:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she for real?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.86,0:16:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check out the back too.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.75,0:17:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it rain last night?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.32,0:17:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, for a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.53,0:17:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would have to open both windows to see the shadow.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.80,0:17:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.97,0:17:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for lunch.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.82,0:17:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all done.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.73,0:17:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having a sister has to be great!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.07,0:17:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you wish that you had a sister?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.16,0:17:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a little bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.28,0:17:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? Did you discover anything?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.11,0:17:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.53,0:17:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're still doing a preliminary investigation.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.31,0:17:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do have a theory though.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.16,0:17:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Let's hear it.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.89,0:17:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you guys talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.89,0:17:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys left me out of the loop.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.92,0:17:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Where do you always sneak off to, anyway?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.55,0:17:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never see you around.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.66,0:17:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.43,0:17:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to take multiple dips on a hot spring trip.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.84,0:17:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how it is?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.29,0:18:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of my yukata?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.55,0:18:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.66,0:18:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look nice!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.52,0:18:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally got my parents to buy one for me at the beginning of summer break.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.26,0:18:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember you've always wanted one.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.63,0:18:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has good taste.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.22,0:18:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with it?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.80,0:18:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sash.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.40,0:18:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it an imitation?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.86,0:18:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is that an abrupt change in a genomic sequence?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.53,0:18:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imitation... not mutation.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.65,0:18:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She used a sash that's not meant to be used for a yukata.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.89,0:18:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't approve of that.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.95,0:18:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's absurd.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.85,0:18:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.18,0:18:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I get cursed by the hanging shadow too?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.01,0:18:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the hot spring we went to yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.35,0:18:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.90,0:18:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hanging shadow.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.94,0:18:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an optical illusion seen by Ibara and Chitanda...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.00,0:18:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Figments of our imagination.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.95,0:18:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it needs a clincher.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.28,0:19:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wait for each other when we're done, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.54,0:19:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.24,0:19:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you eating with us just now?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.69,0:19:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you get here?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.40,0:19:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I took a shortcut right behind the entrance. You can slide down this resorts little cliff at the back.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.28,0:19:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy slid down a cliff just to take a shortcut?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.31,0:19:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I not surprised?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.72,0:19:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't come up with an explanation good enough to satisfy Chitanda.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.65,0:19:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow's identity isn't hard to figure out.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.82,0:19:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The question is why it happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.20,0:19:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you about to pass out from the heat again, Houtarou?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.41,0:19:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were there any special events last night?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.83,0:19:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You passing out from the heat.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.46,0:19:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.95,0:19:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we shared ghost stories.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.53,0:19:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like a pimp, having more girls \Nthan I could wrap my arms around.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.38,0:19:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm talking about official events.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.75,0:19:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there was a summer festival.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.13,0:20:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear the drums?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.16,0:20:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drums...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.14,0:20:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! A summer festival!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.42,0:20:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all clicks.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.81,0:20:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And? What about it?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.22,0:20:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hanging shadow...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.47,0:20:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,must have been a yukata on a hanger.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.10,0:20:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.70,0:20:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would anyone hang a yukata there?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.98,0:20:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it doesn't make sense for anyone to open the windows just to show it to us.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.62,0:20:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't done to show you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.25,0:20:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.28,0:20:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone was drying a wet yukata.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.76,0:20:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The windows were opened for \Nventilation and to dry it more quickly.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.51,0:20:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.23,0:20:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it rained.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.43,0:20:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, why was it in room seven?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.42,0:20:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that it wouldn't be seen.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.22,0:20:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we saw it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.63,0:20:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was meant to be hidden from the family.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.33,0:21:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.09,0:21:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Kayo who put up that yukata to dry.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.00,0:21:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was envious of Rie's yukata, and wanted to wear it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.90,0:21:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt Rie would let her borrow it, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.90,0:21:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? They're sisters.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.07,0:21:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you notice?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.85,0:21:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her cup, stretching card, and bowling ball...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.31,0:21:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{jibun}She's a girl who makes her own things identifiable.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.87,0:21:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo couldn't ask a girl like that to borrow a yukata.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.52,0:21:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.51,0:21:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kayo wanted to wear it no matter what.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.59,0:21:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she took it out, and wore it for the summer festival last night.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.86,0:21:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She left at 8 PM.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.77,0:21:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo went to the summer festival?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.73,0:21:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a glimpse of someone \Nleaving the place at 8 PM yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.36,0:21:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo wasn't there for ghost stories, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.26,0:21:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, she wasn't.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.87,0:21:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, a misfortune befell her.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.25,0:21:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It rained.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.75,0:21:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rain didn't last long, but the yukata got all wet.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.93,0:22:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She remembered the fireworks we were planning for the next day.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.19,0:22:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rie would almost certainly want to wear the yukata for fireworks.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.17,0:22:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had to dry it somehow before the next day or Rie would have found out.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.78,0:22:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be found in the main building's first floor.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.96,0:22:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The annex is out of the question.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.52,0:22:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She couldn't use the dryer at night either.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.78,0:22:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she waited until everyone fell  asleep to hang the yukata to dry.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.03,0:22:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her misfortune continued.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.87,0:22:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moonlight shone through the open \Nwindows, revealing the hanging shadow.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.75,0:22:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{soshite0}The final misfortune is the fact that we're investigating the hanging shadow.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:39.04,0:22:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo must have felt like a cornered rat.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.34,0:22:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The presence I felt back then must have been Kayo.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:47.21,0:22:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:49.17,0:22:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She returned the yukata early in the morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:51.90,0:22:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike Rie, she does stretches \Nearly in the morning every day.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:55.47,0:22:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been easy for her to return it.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:59.17,0:23:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:00.73,0:23:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep this from Ibara.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:03.46,0:23:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll probably create complications.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.19,0:23:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's true...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:11.14,0:23:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must not get along very well.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:16.15,0:23:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine having a sister who you can't even borrow a yukata from.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:27.38,0:23:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that how siblings usually act?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:29.84,0:23:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{watashi}I wanted a sibling.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.35,0:23:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{sonkei}A big sister I could respect, or a cute little brother.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:41.80,0:23:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sibling in Chitanda's ideals...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:45.53,0:23:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be nothing more than a figment of her imagination.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:50.59,0:23:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:55.83,0:23:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:57.02,0:23:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.42,0:24:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe it's not entirely a figment of her imagination.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:50.65,0:25:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next week: Let's Go See an Advanced Screening!
